    "facility": "GKN Aerospace, Garden Grove, CA",
    "started_iso": "2026-05-21T22:40:00Z",
    "status_headline": "Incident resolved: all evacuation orders lifted May 27 at 7:30 PM PDT. EPA confirmed zero air quality exceedances throughout the 7-day incident. Hazmat crews treating remaining solidified MMA in 300-ft exclusion zone on Western Ave. DA criminal investigation ongoing; residents demand GKN accountability. GGUSD schools reopened today (final school day of year). FEMA individual assistance available; call 714-741-5444.",
